<p style="text-align: justify;">What are the main requirements in order to redeem the cash that you earn from PTC?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Basically we have this what they called PayPal, an Electronic Commerce which is free to everyone. You can sign-up by going to their main website “paypal.com” or just Click <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.paypal.com" target="_blank">Here</a> to go to their site. Just Remember to be honest with all the information’s that you will provide in the sign-up form for this is where your earnings will be deposited. Feel free to ask the author when you have questions. You can e-mail me at <a href="mailto:adriangana@gmail.com">adriangana@gmail.com</a>, or you can just simply ask by adding up your queries to the comment box.</p>
