      <title>THE SECRET TO GAIN WISDOM IS “U_D_R_T_N_I_G”</title>
      <link>http://www.oncesaidbythewise.com/the-secret-to-gain-wisdom</link>
      <comments>http://www.oncesaidbythewise.com/the-secret-to-gain-wisdom#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Jul 2010 08:19:15 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>up quotes</dc:creator>
